      <title>希尔豪斯（Hillhouse）寻求再融资床垫制造商的8亿美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/hillhouse-seeks-to-refinance-mattress-maker-s-800-million-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，希尔豪斯（Hillhouse）投资正在与银行进行一次对8亿美元的贷款进行再融资，以支持其对中国床垫制造商AI梦的收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/hillhouse-seeks-to-refinance-mattress-maker-s-800-million-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 01:28:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼债券计划激发了对治理，货币化的恐惧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/indonesian-bond-plan-sparks-fears-over-governance-monetization</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚银行购买将由政府发行的债券资助其雄心勃勃的住房计划的计划，这引起了人们对该国债务治理的更多关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/indonesian-bond-plan-sparks-fears-over-governance-monetization</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 01:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
